data.title: Darlington Borough Council
data.meta_description: Welcome to the Darlington Borough Council web app, report issues, see what's happening in town and lots more.
data.text:
Welcome to the new DBC web app. This app is being actively developed so some features are not fully complete at the moment.

A full list of what is currently working is avalable on our Release Notes page.

Bugs and general comments can be left on our Feedback form.

The leave feedback link in the yellow bar at the bottom of each page will popup this message again if you want to leave some feedback or report a bug.
